channel.title: Comments on: VIDEO: Bad Lieutenant “Sink or Swim”

item.title: By: Surat
item.dc:creator: Surat
item.description: Don't be fooled by this review, the new album by this group is Very good, if you like great guitars, synths and great melodies you will love it. I was fortunate to listen to the promo version of this album and it is very good, very New Orderish.
item.content:encoded: Don’t be fooled by this review, the new album by this group is Very good, if you like great guitars, synths and great melodies you will love it. I was fortunate to listen to the promo version of this album and it is very good, very New Orderish.
